  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的入口控制器流程图，核心是负载均衡器到工作节点的流量路径。起点是c1，一个决策节点，判断请求是否走特定路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，c1用菱形表示决策。那c2是另一个负载均衡器实例吗？我看你写了两个负载均衡器节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c2",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，c1是决策点，c2是实际的负载均衡器服务。当c1判断为Yes时，流量进入c2；判断为No时，直接走c6这个入口控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c2",
        "c6",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出c1到c6的No分支，以及c1到c2的Yes分支。接下来c2之后是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c2",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "c2之后有个No分支，指向c5，这是另一个入口控制器。然后c5要连到c6。同时c2还有条路径要经过工作节点c3和c4。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c5",
        "c6",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "c3和c4都是工作节点，它们之间是串联关系吗？c3连c4，然后c4再连回c1？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c1",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，c3到c4再到c1形成一条环路。这是为了表示工作节点处理完后可能回到决策点重新判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c1",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加c3和c4的串联结构，以及c4到c1的连接。现在检查分支标签：c1到c2是Yes，c2到c5是No，c1到c6也是No，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c2",
        "c5",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，c2到c5的分支标签我刚才说错了，应该是No。但c2到c3的路径不需要标签，那是主流程。让我再确认：c2的Yes分支其实是指向c3这条工作节点链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c5"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，c2的Yes分支指向c3（无标签），c2的No分支指向c5（标签No）。那c5到c6也不需要标签，直接连接？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c5",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，c5到c6直接连。另外最后导出的时候，我需要svg和png两个版本，png要2400宽度透明背景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c5",
